title: Ennio Morricone - Danger Diabolik - OST
description:
In psychedelic swinging 60s style, the dreaded thief (and killer) Diabolik wreaks havoc on a generic European country for his own financial gain and amusement. He shares an extravagant underground lair (and a giant bed of money) with his curvaceous, superficial girlfriend...who uses her awesome powers of wig-wearing to help Diabolik kill innocent people and steal billions from the government. Nonetheless, Diabolik is the &quot;hero&quot; of the film because he must face off against bumbling cops and revenge-seeking mafiosos.
